videos.headline: Northwestern RB takes it up the gut for 3-yd TD
videos.description: Northwestern RB Isaiah Bowser powers through the line for a 3-yard touchdown, giving the Wildcats a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Rutgers RB finds a hole for 44-yard TD
videos.description: Rutgers RB Isaih Pacheco finds open field and takes it 44 yards for a touchdown to give Rutgers the lead 10-7.

videos.headline: Northwestern QB Thorson sacked in end zone for safety
videos.description: Rutgers DB Willington Previlon takes down Wildcats QB Clayton Thorson for an 11-yard loss and a safety.
